sequenceDiagram
    participant ST as Smoke Test Script
    participant EA as Egress Auto-Approver
    participant V6S as v6 Server
    participant RN as Relay Node<br/>(TesRelayManager)
    participant KC as Keycloak
    participant DARE as DARE Submission API
    participant MIO as MinIO
    participant TRE as TRE Agent
    participant FNL as Funnel<br/>(TES executor)
    participant EG as Data Egress API

    ST->>EA: Start as subprocess
    activate EA

    ST->>V6S: POST /api/task (create task)
    V6S-->>ST: task_id=1, status=pending

    V6S--)RN: WebSocket: new_task event
    activate RN

    RN->>KC: Password-grant token (Dare-Control realm)
    KC-->>RN: access_token

    RN->>DARE: GET /api/Project/GetProject?projectId=1
    DARE-->>RN: project (submissionBucket=...)

    RN->>MIO: POST /api/Project/UploadToMinio (algorithm input)
    MIO-->>RN: 200 OK

    RN->>DARE: POST /v1/tasks (TES task creation)
    DARE-->>RN: submission_id=15

    RN->>V6S: PATCH /api/run/1 (status=ACTIVE)

    Note over DARE: Camunda workflow starts

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over DARE,FNL: DARE 5 Safes Pipeline (~40s)
        DARE->>DARE: Parent status: 0 (WaitingForChildren)<br/>Child status: 1 (WaitingForAgent)
        TRE->>DARE: GET GetWaitingSubmissionsForTre
        DARE-->>TRE: child submission
        TRE->>FNL: Submit task to Funnel
        FNL->>FNL: Pull algorithm image<br/>Run container with base32-encoded env vars
        FNL-->>TRE: Execution complete
        TRE->>DARE: Update child status: 38 (DataOutRequested)
        DARE->>EG: Create egress request
    end

    loop Poll every 3s
        EA->>KC: Password-grant token (Data-Egress realm)
        KC-->>EA: access_token
        EA->>EG: GET GetAllEgresses?unprocessedonly=true
        EG-->>EA: pending egress (status=0)
        EA->>EG: POST CompleteEgress (approve all files)
        EG-->>EA: 200 OK
    end

    Note over DARE: Egress approved -> child status: 11 (Completed)<br/>-> parent status: 11 (Completed)

    loop Poll every 5s
        RN->>DARE: GET /api/Submission/GetAllSubmissions
        DARE-->>RN: dare_status=11
        Note over RN: Maps dare_status=11 -> COMPLETE
    end

    RN->>V6S: PATCH /api/run/1 (status=completed, result=TES metadata)
    deactivate RN

    loop Poll every 5s
        ST->>V6S: GET /api/task/1
        V6S-->>ST: status=completed
    end

    ST->>EA: SIGINT (stop)
    deactivate EA
    Note over ST: === SMOKE TEST PASSED ===
